# packages/* conventions

## Allowed dependencies

- `runtime-oss` → `@aucobot/runtime-contracts` only
- Future `database` → Prisma client only
- Future `workspace-sync` → Node fs/path; **no** `@nestjs/*`

## Forbidden in packages/*

- `@nestjs/common`, `@nestjs/core`, Fastify, Express adapters
- Import from `apps/api` or `apps/web`
- Import from sibling `cloud/packages/*` (OSS packages stay public)

## Nest exceptions stay in apps/api

- `BadRequestException`, guards, cookies → map errors at app boundary
- Example: catch `GatewayConfigError` → `BadRequestException` in `apps/api/.../gateway-endpoint.ts`

## Package scaffold

Each package needs: `package.json` (main/types/exports), `tsconfig.json`, `src/index.ts`, `build` script.

After extract: delete duplicate from `apps/api`; update `deploy/Dockerfile.api` if package is in api build graph.
